{"article_id":"YHlrjAgIgAQACBCg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate judiciary committee released 2,500 pages of testimony with Trump ' s son and others","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"who met with Russian attorney at Trump Tower","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"The Trump Organization coordinated with Russians","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"involved in a notorious 2016 meeting at Trump Tower","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"on what to tell the public about the discussions ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"according to emails","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"published by Congress .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The documents show","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that attorneys for the Trump family ' s corporation contacted attendees of the meeting","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"before and after it was revealed by the media ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"in an attempt to manage the response .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"One of the attorneys gave an entire prepared statement to a publicist for the Russian businessman","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"who requested the meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"it \" would be our preference \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"if he did not say anything else to the press .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Donald Trump Jr agreed to the meeting","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"after being told the businessman would supply damaging information from the Russian government about Hillary Clinton , his father ' s opponent in the 2016 presidential campaign .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"The new information was included among 2,500 documents","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"published on Wednesday by the Senate judiciary committee ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"which has been investigating possible collusion between Donald Trump ' s 2016 presidential campaign and Russia .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Profile","depth":3},{"id":22,"text":"Donald Trump Jr","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Show Hide","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Born 31 December 1977 in Manhattan","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"31 December 1977 in Manhattan","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Career","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"After brief stint bartending in Aspen ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he moved back to New York","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to join the Trump Organization ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"supervising Trump Park Avenue and other projects .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"He took an interest in other family enterprises in later years ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"appearing as a guest adviser on his father ' s reality television show The Apprentice and as a judge of various Miss USA pageants .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"After brief stint bartending in Aspen , he moved back to New York","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to join the Trump Organization ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"supervising Trump Park Avenue and other projects .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"He took an interest in other family enterprises in later years ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"appearing as a guest adviser on his father ' s reality television show The Apprentice and as a judge of various Miss USA pageants .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"High point","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Just before the news of his meeting with the Russian lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya , he was riding high as executive director of The Trump Organization and one of the president ' s closest confidants .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Just before the news of his meeting with the Russian lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya , he was riding high as executive director of The Trump Organization and one of the president ' s closest confidants .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Low point","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"On Tuesday 11 July 2017 , he produced the most damning evidence yet in the FBI ' s investigation of Russian meddling in the US election ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"catapulting himself on to the international stage with emails showing","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"he knowingly met with a Russian lawyer","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"claiming to have \" dirt \" on his father ' s rival .","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"On Tuesday 11 July 2017 , he produced the most damning evidence yet in the FBI ' s investigation of Russian meddling in the US election ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"catapulting himself on to the international stage with emails showing","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"he knowingly met with a Russian lawyer","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"claiming to have \" dirt \" on his father ' s rival .","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"He says","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"\" I think","depth":16},{"id":52,"text":"I probably got a lot of my father ' s natural security , or ego , or whatever ...","depth":17},{"id":53,"text":"I can be my own person","depth":18},{"id":54,"text":"and not have to live under his shadow .","depth":18},{"id":55,"text":"I definitely look up to him in many ways","depth":16},{"id":56,"text":"- I ' d like to be more like him","depth":18},{"id":57,"text":"when it comes to business -","depth":18},{"id":58,"text":"but I think","depth":19},{"id":59,"text":"I ' m such a different person ,","depth":19},{"id":60,"text":"it ' s hard to even compare us .","depth":18},{"id":61,"text":"His work persona is kind of what he is .","depth":17},{"id":62,"text":"I have a work face ,","depth":18},{"id":63,"text":"and then there ' s my private life , \"","depth":18},{"id":64,"text":"- Trump Jr to New York magazine , 2004 .","depth":16},{"id":65,"text":"\" I think","depth":17},{"id":66,"text":"I probably got a lot of my father ' s natural security , or ego , or whatever ...","depth":17},{"id":67,"text":"I can be my own person","depth":17},{"id":68,"text":"and not have to live under his shadow .","depth":17},{"id":69,"text":"I definitely look up to him in many ways -","depth":17},{"id":70,"text":"I ' d like to be more like him","depth":18},{"id":71,"text":"when it comes to business -","depth":18},{"id":72,"text":"but I think","depth":18},{"id":73,"text":"I ' m such a different person ,","depth":18},{"id":74,"text":"it ' s hard to even compare us .","depth":17},{"id":75,"text":"His work persona is kind of what he is .","depth":16},{"id":76,"text":"I have a work face ,","depth":17},{"id":77,"text":"and then there ' s my private life , \"","depth":17},{"id":78,"text":"- Trump Jr to New York magazine , 2004 .","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"They say","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"\" It ' s a do-anything-you-can-to-win world","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"that he ' s part of ,","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"and his eagerness","depth":20},{"id":83,"text":"to meet with this lawyer ,","depth":20},{"id":84,"text":"who was very explicitly described as having information","depth":21},{"id":85,"text":"that came from Russian government sources","depth":21},{"id":86,"text":"- there ' s no mystery there .","depth":20},{"id":87,"text":"There ' s no veil .","depth":20},{"id":88,"text":"There ' s not even one veil .","depth":20},{"id":89,"text":"Her name wasn ' t mentioned","depth":21},{"id":90,"text":"but everything else was very explicit","depth":21},{"id":91,"text":"and he leaps at it .","depth":20},{"id":92,"text":"That ' s all part of this all-that-matters-is-winning ,","depth":21},{"id":93,"text":"there ' s winning","depth":22},{"id":94,"text":"and there ' s losing ,","depth":22},{"id":95,"text":"that ' s it .","depth":20},{"id":96,"text":"That ' s the value system","depth":19},{"id":97,"text":"and in that way , he very much echoes his father. \"","depth":18},{"id":98,"text":"- Gwenda Blair , Trump biographer , to , 12 July 2017 .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"\" It ' s a do-anything-you-can-to-win world","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"that he ' s part of ,","depth":16},{"id":101,"text":"and his eagerness","depth":20},{"id":102,"text":"to meet with this lawyer ,","depth":20},{"id":103,"text":"who was very explicitly described as having information","depth":20},{"id":104,"text":"that came from Russian government sources","depth":20},{"id":105,"text":"- there ' s no mystery there .","depth":18},{"id":106,"text":"There ' s no veil .","depth":19},{"id":107,"text":"There ' s not even one veil .","depth":19},{"id":108,"text":"Her name wasn ' t mentioned","depth":20},{"id":109,"text":"but everything else was very explicit","depth":20},{"id":110,"text":"and he leaps at it .","depth":19},{"id":111,"text":"That ' s all part of this all-that-matters-is-winning ,","depth":19},{"id":112,"text":"there ' s winning","depth":20},{"id":113,"text":"and there ' s losing ,","depth":20},{"id":114,"text":"that ' s it .","depth":18},{"id":115,"text":"That ' s the value system","depth":18},{"id":116,"text":"and in that way , he very much echoes his father. \"","depth":18},{"id":117,"text":"- Gwenda Blair , Trump biographer , to , 12 July 2017 .","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"The Trump Tower meeting is a key flashpoint for congressional investigators and Robert Mueller , the special counsel ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"who is also looking into possible collusion .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"US intelligence concluded","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"the Kremlin intervened","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"to help Trump beat Clinton .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Trump Jr , along with Trump ' s son-in-law Jared Kushner and the 2016 presidential campaign chairman Paul Manafort , met a group","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"including Natalia Veselnitskaya , a Kremlin-connected lawyer ,","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"at the campaign headquarters on 9 June 2016 .","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"Mueller is also investigating","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"whether Trump or his associates tried to obstruct justice through various actions","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"since the inquiries began .","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"Trump and his attorneys deny any wrongdoing","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"and have dismissed the investigation as a witch-hunt .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"After news of the meeting broke in July ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Alan Futerfas , an attorney for the Trump Organization , emailed the publicist , Rob Goldstone , a proposed statement in Goldstone ' s name .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"The statement supported Trump Jr ' s account of the meeting as a \" complete waste of time \"","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"which had focused on policy issues such as economic sanctions and a ban on Americans","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"adopting Russian children .","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"\" If you feel comfortable with this statement","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"and are comfortable saying nothing more ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"at least for the time being ,","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"that would be our preference , \"","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"said Futerfas .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"\" Again , any statement should be accurate as to your very best recollection . \"","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Ike Kaveladze , a Russian businessman","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"who attended the meeting ,","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"testified to the committee","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"that Futerfas ' s proposed statement failed to mention","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"that issues around the US Democratic party had been discussed in the meeting .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"But he and others denied","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"that \" dirt \" on Clinton came up .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"Futerfas spoke several times with Kaveladze by telephone","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"before the meeting was made public ,","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"according to the emails ,","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"and was due to speak with Emin Agalarov , the Russian businessman and singer","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"represented by Goldstone .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Emin ' s father , Aras Agalarov , is a Russian developer on good terms with Vladimir Putin .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Alan Garten , another Trump Organization attorney , spoke by telephone with Goldstone in the weeks","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"before the news broke .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"Following the call ,","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"Goldstone wrote in an email :","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"\" They are concerned","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"because it Jinks","depth":18},{"id":161,"text":"[ sic ]","depth":18},{"id":162,"text":"Don Jr to officials from Russia","depth":17},{"id":163,"text":"- which he has always denied meeting . \"","depth":16},{"id":164,"text":"Garten was due to call Kaveladze as well ,","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"according to the emails .","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"Another email from July 2017 showed the incoming White House communications director , Anthony Scaramucci telling Goldstone","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"it was important that \" we remain consistent and united \" in the face of public pressure about the meeting .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"In a statement on Wednesday , Democratic senators on the committee said","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"the records showed","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"Trump ' s team were left \" frustrated and angry \"","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"that the meeting did not produce enough damaging information on Clinton .","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"\" Their efforts","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"to conceal the meeting and its true purpose","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"are consistent with a larger pattern of false statements about the Trump campaign ' s relationship with Russia , \"","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"the Democrats said .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"Goldstone emailed Trump Jr , purportedly on behalf of Emin Agalarov ,","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"to arrange the meeting at Trump Tower ,","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"that his clients had information on Clinton from the Russian government .","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"The released documents show","depth":14},{"id":181,"text":"that Goldstone forwarded Futerfas ' s email about the proposed statement on 10 July to Kaveladze , one of Aras Agalarov ' s executives ,","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"who attended the meeting at Trump Tower .","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"\" Here is statement by Trump lawyers","depth":15},{"id":184,"text":"which they have asked me to release , \"","depth":15},{"id":185,"text":"Goldstone wrote in the subject bar .","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"Kaveladze and Futerfas then exchanged emails","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"apparently arranging a call .","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"The Trump attorney had already emailed Emin Agalarov on 30 June","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"asking Agalarov to contact him .","depth":15},{"id":190,"text":"\" Can you please give me a call at your convenience regarding certain matters , \"","depth":15},{"id":191,"text":"Futerfas said .","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"Text messages in Russian","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"released by the committee","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"showed","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"Kaveladze and Veselnitskaya , the Kremlin-connected lawyer , sought another meeting with Trump ' s team after the 2016 election","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"but found doors closed to them .","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"The pair also discussed the public reaction in the US to the Trump-Russia saga .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"Of a dossier","depth":16},{"id":199,"text":"alleging","depth":17},{"id":200,"text":"that Trump took part in an orgy in a Moscow hotel ,","depth":17},{"id":201,"text":"Kaveladze wrote :","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"\" It ' s nonsense .","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"I can myself say as witness","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"that nothing like that happened during the Miss Universe contest in Moscow . \"","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"The records show","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"that Goldstone also offered to arrange a meeting between Trump and Putin less than six weeks into Trump ' s presidential campaign .","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"The publicist suggested in a July 2015 email to Rhona Graff , Trump ' s executive assistant ,","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"that Trump may \" welcome a meeting with President Putin ,","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"which Emin would set up \" .","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"There was no indication","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"the offer was accepted .","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"The transcripts also show","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"that Trump Jr told the committee","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"that he couldn ' t remember","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"whether he had discussed the Russia investigation with his father .","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"Trump Jr also deflected a question","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"on whether his father had been involved in drafting the Trump team ' s official statement on the meeting ,","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"which claimed","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"it was a policy discussion with little relevance to the presidential campaign .","depth":13},{"id":220,"text":"Profile","depth":4},{"id":221,"text":"Who is Natalia Veselnitskaya ?","depth":6},{"id":222,"text":"Show Hide","depth":6},{"id":223,"text":"Accusations","depth":6},{"id":224,"text":"Natalia Veselnitskaya is the Russian lawyer","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"who met with Donald Trump Jr , Jared Kushner and Paul Manafort at Trump Tower on 9 June 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"Trump Jr has published emails","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"showing Veselnitskaya was introduced to him as a \" Russian government attorney \"","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"who had damaging information about Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"Background","depth":5},{"id":230,"text":"Veselnitskaya is a defence lawyer","depth":7},{"id":231,"text":"based just outside Moscow ,","depth":7},{"id":232,"text":"whose main client in recent years has been Denis Katsyv , a businessman","depth":8},{"id":233,"text":"accused of profiting from a major tax fraud","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"uncovered by lawyer Sergei Magnitsky .","depth":9},{"id":235,"text":"She fought his case in US courts","depth":8},{"id":236,"text":"and mounted a PR campaign","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"to try to clear Katsyv ' s name","depth":10},{"id":238,"text":"and overturn the \" Magnitsky Act \" sanctions against Russian officials","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"that followed .","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"The big question","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"Veselnitskaya is not a government official","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"and portrays herself as a lawyer with a private client .","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"The question , then , is how she was able to secure the meeting at Trump Tower during a presidential campaign","depth":8},{"id":244,"text":"and why she was introduced to Trump Jr","depth":9},{"id":245,"text":"as representing the Russian government .","depth":9},{"id":246,"text":"Reports have said","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"the president took a direct role in the preparation of the statement .","depth":10},{"id":248,"text":"Mueller is understood to want to ask Trump about his involvement .","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"Asked in the interview","depth":10},{"id":250,"text":"if his father was involved in drafting the statement ,","depth":10},{"id":251,"text":"Trump said :","depth":10},{"id":252,"text":"\" I don ' t know .","depth":11},{"id":253,"text":"I never spoke to my father about it . \"","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"According to the transcripts ,","depth":8},{"id":255,"text":"Trump Jr also said","depth":9},{"id":256,"text":"he didn ' t think","depth":10},{"id":257,"text":"there was anything wrong","depth":11},{"id":258,"text":"with attending the Trump Tower meeting","depth":12},{"id":259,"text":"in which he was promised dirt on Hillary Clinton .","depth":12},{"id":260,"text":"On Wednesday Trump Jr said in a statement","depth":7},{"id":261,"text":"that he was \" candid and forthright \" in his interview with the committee .","depth":7},{"id":262,"text":"Goldstone told the committee","depth":8},{"id":263,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":264,"text":"the meeting was a \" bad idea \" .","depth":9},{"id":265,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":266,"text":"he reported back to Emin Agalarov","depth":10},{"id":267,"text":"that \" this was the most embarrassing thing","depth":11},{"id":268,"text":"you ' ve ever asked me to do .","depth":11},{"id":269,"text":"I ' ve just sat in a meeting about adoption . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":539,"left":290,"right":538,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":271,"right":289,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":284,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":275,"right":283,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":273,"right":274,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":272,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":278,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":7,"right":277,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":277,"left":276,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":279,"right":281,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":13,"right":280,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":285,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":18,"right":286,